[Error] The Stateflow chart InductiveChargingStateMachine has a State-vs.-Transition ratio of 7.767%, which is below the threshold of 10%.
[Whitelisted] This check was introduced late in the project. To solve this finding a thoroughly analysis of all affected statemachines is needed as start to rework them. This has a high possibility to break functionality and is therefore not recommend at the moment.

[Error] transition [ Reset || (after(Timeout , tick)) ] located in Timer uses an argument which is not uint.
[Whitelisted] The data type of the first argument must be uint32, but this parameter has a different data type. This error happens from the begining of Gen5, the datatype have never been changed, there is no known issues in the code generation to date and changing all this parameters will be a lot of effort. They will be updated if there is a technical reason. Also the change from uint16 to uint32 will take more memory.
